<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَسَادُ الْإِجَارَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>جَهَالَةُ قَدْرِ الْمَنْفَعَةِ فِي عَقْدِ الْإِجَارَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(س)</span> , عَنْ يُونُسَ، عَنْ الْحَسَنِ أَنَّهُ كَرِهَ أَنْ يَسْتَأجِرَ الرَّجُلَ حَتَّى يُعْلِمَهُ أَجْرَهُ. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) (س) ٣٨٥٨ , (ن) ٤٦٧٤</p> </div>